Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Thursday! I have a quick one for you today, all in service of making =
Not Boring more valuable to you, a better business, and better at supportin=
g our portfolio companies.
We=E2=80=99ll hit three things:
Not Boring Survey: It=E2=80=99s been a minute since we=E2=80=99ve done one =
of these, and we=E2=80=99d love to learn more about you, what you=E2=80=99r=
e looking to get out of Not Boring, and what we can do better.
Not Boring Talent Collective: We now have over 500 people in the Not Boring=
 Talent Collective =E2=80=94 if you=E2=80=99re looking to get a new job at =
the type of companies I write about in Not Boring, or if you=E2=80=99re loo=
