focused Not Boring Founders Podcast with the support of our Season 2 Presen=
ting Sponsor, FTX US, and I=E2=80=99d love for you to check it out, subscri=
be, rate, and most importantly, give me feedback.
That=E2=80=99s it. Short and Sweet.
Let=E2=80=99s get to it.
Three Not Boring Things
